---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service - ByteLite" description="ByteLite terms of service for ByteLite compression, Deep Kore / AIya, and HeartStrings. Usage guidelines, licensing terms, and legal information.">
  <section class="legal-page">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="legal-content">
        <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
        <p class="last-updated">Last updated: April 18, 2026</p>

        <h2>Acceptance of Terms</h2>
        <p>By accessing and using ByteLite services, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service and all applicable laws and regulations.</p>

        <h2>Deep Kore Lab</h2>
        <p>The Deep Kore Lab at /deepkore-lab is a public research environment. By submitting prompts to the Deep Kore Lab, you agree to the following:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Interactions may be stored and used for system improvement.</strong> Prompts submitted through the Deep Kore Lab are logged and may be included in nightly learning updates for the Deep Kore / AIya system.</li>
          <li><strong>No expectation of identical responses across builds.</strong> The Deep Kore system updates nightly. The same prompt may produce a different response after a nightly build runs. This is by design.</li>
          <li><strong>Research environment.</strong> The Deep Kore Lab is a research environment, not a production consumer service. Responses, when available, reflect the current deterministic build state.</li>
          <li><strong>No sensitive information.</strong> Do not submit sensitive, confidential, personal, or identifying information through the Deep Kore Lab. ByteLite LLC is not responsible for information you choose to submit.</li>
          <li><strong>Prohibited content.</strong> Do not submit content that is unlawful, harmful, threatening, abusive, harassing, defamatory, or otherwise objectionable. The system will refuse unsafe queries and log the refusal.</li>
          <li><strong>No live AI responses currently.</strong> The Deep Kore runtime is not yet publicly deployed. Prompt submissions are queued. The lab does not generate real-time responses at this time.</li>
          <li><strong>Reasonable use.</strong> Do not use automated tools to flood the submission queue. Rate limits apply.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>License Terms</h2>
        <p>ByteLite's compression technology is protected by pending patents. Use of our technology requires a valid license agreement.</p>

        <h2>Restrictions</h2>
        <p>You may not reverse engineer, decompile, or disassemble the ByteLite technology, except to the extent that such activity is expressly permitted by applicable law.</p>

        <h2>Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>ByteLite and all related trademarks, service marks, and logos are the property of ByteLite LLC. Patent pending.</p>

        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>For questions about these Terms, please contact us at <a href="mailto:legal@thebytelite.com">legal@thebytelite.com</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal-page {
    padding: 2.5rem 0;
    min-height: 60vh;
  }

  .legal-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .legal-content h1 {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .legal-content h2 {
    margin: 3rem 0 1rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .legal-content p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .legal-content a {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .legal-content a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .last-updated {
    font-style: italic;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
</style>

